### MCP Server HTTP Testing
### Test MCP JSON-RPC 2.0 Protocol
### Use for manual testing via IntelliJ HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Tools List - Discover all available tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {},
  "id": 1
}

